snippet.title: HOLMGANG: Memories of the Forgotten -  Teaser Trailer - English
snippet.description: "Forge your own legend. Live the dark days of the Shadow War. Fight to regain your honor as the Ronin Tatsu. Fight to avenge the death of your family as the Barbarian Kandar. Fight to take your place as the Amazon Valentia. Join the fight against the empire of Hazulem and his Shadow Demons and change the course of history forever "
